    <item>
      <title>苹果寻求从中国反垄断应用程序裁决中剔除“市场主导地位”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/apple-seeks-to-scrub-dominance-from-china-antitrust-app-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 正寻求让中国一家法院改变其在 iPhone 制造商赢得的诉讼中的书面裁决，这一不同寻常的举动凸显了这家美国公司在全球最大智能手机领域的地位的敏感性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/apple-seeks-to-scrub-dominance-from-china-antitrust-app-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 03:50:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能需求旺盛，韩国大幅上调经济增长预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/south-korea-hikes-economic-forecasts-sharply-as-ai-fuels-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球对人工智能的需求旺盛，推动韩国半导体出口达到创纪录水平，韩国大幅上调了经济增长预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/south-korea-hikes-economic-forecasts-sharply-as-ai-fuels-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 03:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芯片制造商瑞萨背后的前银行家追逐 1000 亿美元市值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/ex-banker-behind-chipmaker-renesas-targets-100-billion-value</link>
      <description><![CDATA[十年前，瑞萨电子公司受政府控制，资金严重短缺。如今，这家日本芯片制造商的市值已达 350 亿美元，通过一系列海外收购，该公司的目标是到 2030 年市值达到 1000 亿美元左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/ex-banker-behind-chipmaker-renesas-targets-100-billion-value</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 01:50:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
